                            <comment id="14079788" author="ppakulski" created="Wed, 30 Jul 2014 19:08:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is due to an incorrect conversion of &lt;b&gt;BlobGcMaxAgeInSecs&lt;/b&gt; parameter (hours are converted to milliseconds instead of seconds). As a result, maxAge is set by default to 1000 days (almost 3 years), instead of 24 hours (1 day).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14079799" author="ppakulski" created="Wed, 30 Jul 2014 19:14:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch attached&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
